Cell[TextData[{
 "For radius 1/1024, it is useful to do an exhaustive search because the \
function is noisy.  We see that we lose about 1 bit compared to the extrema \
found by ",
 StyleBox["FindMaximum", "Code"],
 ", but we are left with 21 bits after the mantissa, which is sufficient:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9253097932916584`*^9, 3.925309821164661*^9}, {
